OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome warm, sunny spells are
OL,6,Fexpected, but with cloud also building
OL,7,Fto bring occasional showers, heavy at
OL,8,Ftimes. Showers becoming blustery
OL,9,Fduring the afternoon. Feeling warm in
OL,10,Fthe sunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMostly cloudy, outbreaks of
OL,13,Frain affecting northern and eastern
OL,14,Fareas, isolated showers elsewhere.
OL,15,FRain clears during the early hours to
OL,16,Fleave clear spells and the odd
OL,17,Fisolated shower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
