OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FOften cloudy Friday, with the
OL,6,Fodd shower particularly during the
OL,7,Fevening, but also some brighter
OL,8,Fspells. Wind freshening through the
OL,9,Fmorning.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRain
OL,12,Flikely Saturday morning, clearing to
OL,13,Fsunny spells and afternoon showers.
OL,14,FDrier and sunnier Sunday with winds
OL,15,Feasing. Cloudier on Monday but
OL,16,Fprobably dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
